[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0992","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10781,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10802}}","description":"HP VirtualVault 安全绕过漏洞，攻击者可利用受信任网关代理（TGP）机制 bypassing 补丁 PHSS_17692 限制，对系统发起非授权访问。该漏洞源于虚拟存储系统身份验证机制缺陷，允许任意未授权进程绕过访问控制，对文件进行非法读写或进行系统操作。攻击者无需具备管理员权限，只需向虚拟存储服务发送特定协议命令，即可取得对安全敏感数据的访问权限，导致企业敏感信息泄露、篡改或被恶意利用。HP 早前曾发布安全补丁，但实际应用中仍存在配置缺陷导致漏洞无法彻底修复，影响范围涵盖 Windows/Linux 多平台虚拟存储环境。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0992"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.707","remediation":"升级 HP VirtualVault 至包含 PHSS_17692 之后修复补丁的版本（如 PHSS_18500 及以上），并通过 Software Distributor 重新安装 TGP 模块。临时缓解：在 Trusted Gateway Proxy 配置中收紧进程访问控制列表，禁止未授权进程建立 TGP 连接，并限制仅允许受信虚拟主体访问代理端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9912-107","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0992","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0992.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c9ec7f26a52f816468b636e23146049097db5070/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4c74-52ch-5mh5/GHSA-4c74-52ch-5mh5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001105.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1609.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0839","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1002","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10768,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10785}}","description":"Netscape Navigator 在存储用户用于访问 Netscape 邮件服务的密码时，采用了强度较弱的加密算法进行保护。由于加密强度不足，本地或具备一定权限的攻击者可通过分析相关存储文件，较容易地还原出明文密码。该漏洞影响使用 Netscape Navigator 邮件功能的用户，攻击条件为攻击者需能访问受害者本地存储的密码数据或取得相应读取权限，利用方式为通过逆向弱加密存储内容获取邮件账户凭据，进而可能危及用户邮件通信安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1002"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.997","remediation":"建议将 Netscape Navigator 升级至 4.7 或更高版本（该版本改进了密码存储加密强度）。如无法立即升级，可在邮件客户端中取消\"记住密码\"选项，改用手动输入，并避免在不信任主机上保存邮件密码；同时在本地系统中对用户配置目录设置严格的文件访问权限以限制密码文件被读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94536309217214&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94570673523998&w=2","http://www.rstcorp.com/news/bad-crypto.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1002","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1002.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88419/info.html","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--d48d045b-59cc-4474-90a9-e6ede9ca2247.owl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1002.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0894","title":"Red Hat Linux screen 程序本地终端写入漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 系统中的 screen 终端复用程序未使用 Unix98 伪终端（ptys），存在安全漏洞。本地攻击者可利用此缺陷，通过 screen 程序向其他用户的终端写入数据，实现终端劫持或注入恶意命令。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需额外认证即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0894"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.680","remediation":"升级 screen 程序至 3.7.6 及以上版本，该版本默认使用 Unix98 ptys 并正确设置终端权限，防止本地用户跨终端写入。如无法升级，可在 screen 配置文件中设置 `perm` 选项限制终端访问，或通过 `chmod 700 /dev/pts/*` 收紧伪终端权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0894","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0894.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b9fb833e196fd08d699d3ef970b517d24cc12600/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0894.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0894","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0894.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0894.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gc92-56cg-2qv2/GHSA-gc92-56cg-2qv2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0894.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001076.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0894.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0876","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 在处理 EMBED 标签时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可构造包含恶意 EMBED 标签的特制网页，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Internet Explorer 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者可通过电子邮件或恶意网站传播利用代码，无需身份认证即可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0876"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.490","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 及以上版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全更新 MS99-037。鉴于 IE 4.0 已停止技术支持，建议升级至 IE 11 或改用 Edge/Chrome 等现代浏览器，同时在 IE 中禁用 ActiveX 控件及 EMBED 标签解析功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ185959","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0876.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0876.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0876","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0876.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0876.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pfw2-q2vc-hgpf/GHSA-pfw2-q2vc-hgpf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0876.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0350","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0735","title":"KDE K-Mail 临时文件符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"KDE K-Mail 存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击在用户临时目录中劫持 K-Mail 创建的临时文件，从而以目标用户权限覆盖或创建任意文件，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.1/1.1.1、Caldera kdenetwork 1.1.1-1、Caldera OpenLinux 1.3/2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地账户访问权限，利用条件为诱使高权限用户运行 K-Mail 并触发临时文件操作。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0735"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.883","remediation":"建议升级 KDE 至 1.1.2 或更高版本，并更新 kdenetwork 软件包以修复 K-Mail 的临时目录符号链接漏洞。作为临时缓解，可为每个用户创建独立且权限受限（0700）的临时目录，避免使用共享的可预测临时路径，并设置 TMPDIR 环境变量指向私有目录，同时开启内核 fs.protected_symlinks 保护以阻止符号链接攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999015_01.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/300","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/37cec437f4ca5dbafb8ef4c4921c71da1b289b8f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0735","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0735.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6q2m-wvf7-77h8/GHSA-6q2m-wvf7-77h8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0350.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0350.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0365","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0365.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0744","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 与 FastTrack Server 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 及 FastTrack Server 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送超长的 HTTP GET 请求触发溢出，从而在服务器上执行任意代码并提升权限。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛低，成功利用后可导致服务器被完全控制、敏感信息泄露及服务中断。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0744"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"2000-01-04","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 与 FastTrack Server 至厂商发布的已修复版本，在补丁部署前可通过反向代理或 WAF 限制过长的 HTTP GET 请求长度，并对 HTTP 请求头字段做长度校验以缓解溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T02:21:21.050767475+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0744","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/603"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0365.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0365.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0365.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0756","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0964","title":"FreeBSD libc setlocale 函数 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统的 libc 库中 setlocale 函数在处理 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过构造超长的 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量值，导致堆栈缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意代码获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 3.x 早期版本，攻击条件为攻击者拥有本地登录权限或能通过其他方式在目标系统上执行程序并控制其环境变量。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0964"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.217","remediation":"立即升级至 FreeBSD 3.4-RELEASE 或更高版本（包括 FreeBSD-SA-00:19 补丁），该补丁修复了 libc 中 setlocale 函数处理 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量时的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法立即升级，可在系统环境变量配置中移除 PATH_LOCALE 变量，或修改启动脚本使用支持边界检查的 locale 设置方式，同时建议检查是否有未授权账户登录痕迹。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6086","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/20b9340dcaffca733259fb153ac741206a5bbc5f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0964.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0964","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0964.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e90735e3e31fc62018265dfbae313d166e653462/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0964.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9w6w-73wp-668p/GHSA-9w6w-73wp-668p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0964.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83054/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1591","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Services 身份验证绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) 4.0 SP4 在未安装特定修补程序的情况下，存在认证绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可在特定条件下绕过身份验证机制，无需提供有效凭据即可访问受保护资源。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，可通过 Microsoft Visual InterDev 6.0 连接触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。微软已发布相关修补程序修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1591"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:47.373","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止支持的 IIS 4.0 SP4，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022 自带 IIS 10），并启用 Windows 身份验证模块，禁用匿名访问。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中为受影响站点启用「集成 Windows 身份验证」并关闭「匿名身份验证」作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998-1999/msg00276.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998-1999/msg00277.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/190","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1591.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1591","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1591.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2853180ecaf9d7461fd6bb98e4528ce223cae51d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1591.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x4j4-xc7j-8rv5/GHSA-x4j4-xc7j-8rv5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1591.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001066.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e271b07-d6b2-41cf-9e3c-457a18fff72f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/visual_interdev_cve.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1588","title":"Sun Solaris x86 nlps_server 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris x86 2.4/2.5/2.5.1 的 nlps_server 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 TCP 2766 端口（System V listener）发送以 \"NLPS:002:002:\" 开头超长字符串触发该漏洞，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris x86 多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1588"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:46.927","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.6 及以上版本以彻底修复 nlps_server 缓冲区溢出漏洞；如无法升级，立即停止 nlps_server 服务（/etc/init.d/nlps stop）并从 inetd.conf 中注释掉相关行，同时在防火墙层面阻断 TCP 端口 2766 的入站流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lsd-pl.net/files/get?SOLARIS/solx86_nlps_server","http://security-protocols.com/sploits/unsorted_exploits/nlps_server.c","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2319","http://www.securityfocus.com/data/vulnerabilities/exploits/nlps_server.c","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20602","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1588.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1588.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1588","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/7945630e737b12fd979f83fb4e5b84193f6c10cf/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1588.json","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-1588_90f8dcbd-6e6a-43b1-ab5b-2370d6ed9641","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1588.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wh9q-9hjg-qw4c/GHSA-wh9q-9hjg-qw4c.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-1588.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001063.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--01db8430-9ac8-47b1-8615-8a9920ff0d0a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2009","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1584","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9157,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10843}}","description":"SunOS 4.1.1 至 4.1.3c 版本中的 loadmodule 程序，以及以 setuid/setgid 权限安装的 modload 程序（含 Open Windows 3.0 中的相关组件）存在未知缺陷。本地已登录的普通用户可通过精心构造环境变量，在调用这些程序时影响其加载模块的行为，从而将自身权限提升至 root。该漏洞仅影响具备本地系统访问权限的用户，无法被远程利用，但一旦成功利用即可完全控制受影响主机，危害等级极高（CVSS 评分 10.0）。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1584"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:46.420","remediation":"建议升级到 SunOS 4.1.4 或更高版本，并安装 Sun 官方提供的 patch 100572/100573 系列补丁修复 loadmodule 与 modload 的权限缺陷。如无法立即升级，应以 root 身份执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/loadmodule 及 chmod u-s /usr/bin/modload 移除其 setuid/setgid 位，并限制普通用户对相关二进制文件的执行权限，避免通过环境变量进行本地提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/search/document.do?assetkey=1-22-00124-1","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-18.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1584.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1584","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1584.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1584.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8jjf-pj37-wq93/GHSA-8jjf-pj37-wq93.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0282.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87932/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1586.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1982","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1982.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1512","title":"AMaViS 病毒扫描器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"AMaViS 病毒扫描器 0.2.0-pre4 及更早版本存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送包含恶意 shell 元字符的感染邮件，并在 Reply-To 字段中嵌入系统命令，当 AMaViS 处理邮件时触发命令执行。由于 AMaViS 以 root 权限运行，攻击者可直接获取服务器完全控制权，造成严重安全威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1512"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:35.963","remediation":"升级 AMaViS 至 0.3.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 reply-to 字段的 shell 元字符过滤逻辑。如无法升级，在 sendmail/procmail 调用链中对邮件头部进行严格过滤，阻止包含 `;`、`|`、`` ` `` 等 shell 元字符的 reply-to 字段进入扫描流程，或改用 amavisd-new 替代旧版 AMaViS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93219846414732&w=2","http://www.amavis.org/ChangeLog.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/527","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2349"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1982.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1324","title":"OpenVMS VAXstations 登录失败锁定机制绕过漏洞","description":"Open VMS VAXstations 5.3 至 5.5-2 版本中，当使用 VMS DECwindows 或 MOTIF 图形界面时，系统未能正确限制超过登录失败阈值的用户账户访问权限。具体而言，当用户账户因多次登录失败触发 break-in 限制后，系统并未实际禁用该账户，导致攻击者可以绕过账户锁定机制持续进行暴力破解密码攻击。该漏洞降低了暴力破解的难度，使远程攻击者更容易通过枚举方式获取系统访问权限，影响所有运行受影响版本 Open VMS 的 VAXstations 设备。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1324"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.863","remediation":"升级 Open VMS 至 5.5-3 或更高版本，该版本已修复登录失败阈值检测失效问题。如无法升级，在 SYLOGIN.COM 或系统登录脚本中增加登录失败计数检查逻辑，并启用 SYSGEN 参数 LGI_BRK_LIM 强制限制。同时配置 INTRUSION_RECORD 启用入侵检测记录，监控异常登录行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-06.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7225","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1324","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_200_300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87872/info.html","https://github.com/jmohitz/SECAI/blob/33119e592f944e313664a5f75ae76284ea4b3fe8/data/CWE/307.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1293","title":"Apache HTTP Server mod_proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及更早版本中的 mod_proxy 模块存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向代理模块发送特制的畸形 FTP 命令，触发 Apache 进程崩溃（dump core），导致服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Apache 1.2.5 及之前版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，危害等级高危。建议升级至 1.3.0 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1293"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.733","remediation":"升级至 Apache 1.3.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 mod_proxy 处理畸形 FTP 命令时的段错误问题。如无法升级，可禁用 mod_proxy 模块（注释 LoadModule proxy_module 行）作为临时缓解措施。另外可配置防火墙限制对 80 端口的非正常 FTP 协议流量访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88413292830649&w=2","http://www.apache.org/info/security_bulletin_1.2.5.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1293","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/Apache%E7%9A%84mod_proxy%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-1293).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1293.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001016.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b57e5b05-d1d6-4263-bf39-3df1599fd25f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1809","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1246","title":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Direct Mailer 密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 的 Direct Mailer 功能存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，该功能将用户域名和密码以纯文本形式保存在 TMLBQueue 网络共享中，且该共享默认权限设置不安全，允许远程攻击者通过网络共享读取明文凭据，进而获取系统权限。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，影响范围广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1246"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.790","remediation":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 已停止支持，建议立即迁移至受支持的邮件服务解决方案。如暂时无法迁移，应严格限制 TMLBQueue 网络共享的访问权限，仅允许授权管理 IP 访问，并启用共享加密或改用安全认证协议（如 NTLMv2）替代明文密码传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q229/9/72.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2068"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1233","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 域名解析访问限制漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在域名解析访问限制绕过漏洞（Domain Resolution）。当用户发起初始会话请求时，若其 IP 地址无法成功解析为 DNS 域名，IIS 未能正确实施访问控制策略，导致远程攻击者可通过使用未注册反向 DNS 记录的 IP 地址绕过身份验证和权限限制，获取对受限资源的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，建议升级至更高版本或部署应用层防火墙进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1233"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.120","remediation":"升级至 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用未解析域名的 IP 访问，或通过配置 URLScan 工具过滤无反向 DNS 记录的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q241/5/62.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/657","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3306"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml"}]